rows.label: qst650313_msg0001
rows.name:
Something on your mind, madam?
Well, worry no more! Kamuya is at
your service!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0002
rows.name:
Anything we can help you fine ladies
with?

rows.label: qst650313_msg0003
rows.name:
Goodness! Far be it from me to pass
up the opportunity to talk to a fine,
strapping young lad!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0004
rows.name: Oh! You flatter me!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0005
rows.name:
Actually, I think she was talking
about me there...

rows.label: qst650313_msg0006
rows.name: You lie!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0007
rows.name:
Oh, please, don't take offense!
You're both very handsome young
men! Regal as His Majesty!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0008
rows.name: All right, I forgive you.

rows.label: qst650313_msg0009
rows.name:
Anyhow, you seemed deep in
thought, madam. Is there any way
we could help you?

rows.label: qst650313_msg0010
rows.name:
Oh, that's right. Perhaps there is,
perhaps there is!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0011
rows.name:
It's the monsters, you see. They're
becoming a dreadful nuisance of late.

rows.label: qst650313_msg0012
rows.name:
I fear it's only a matter time before
some poor soul is attacked when
they're out foraging for supplies...

rows.label: qst650313_msg0013
rows.name:
Well, if it's monster slaying you're
after, look no further!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0014
rows.name:
You're a real show stealer, aren't
you Kamuya, old chum?

rows.label: qst650313_msg0015
rows.name:
Just be wary of the old dame.
I'm not sure you know what you've
let yourself in for...

rows.label: qst650313_msg0016
rows.name:
Haha, well...let's cross that bridge
when we come to it, all right?

rows.label: qst650313_msg0017
rows.name: Oh, it's so sweet of you to help, boys...

rows.label: qst650313_msg0018
rows.name:
I wonder if you could help get rid of
some Grad Gogol around the Genbu
Drifts area...

rows.label: qst650313_msg0019
rows.name:
Getting rid of some Vint Griffox would
be lovely too, while you're at it.

rows.label: qst650313_msg0020
rows.name:
They could handle that Bland Upa
situation as well, couldn't they?

rows.label: qst650313_msg0021
rows.name:
And don't forget the Arno Kapiba!
They're getting very out of hand!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0022
rows.name: Um...can I ask something as well?

rows.label: qst650313_msg0023
rows.name: Fire away, little buddy!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0024
rows.name:
Okay... Could you finish off some
Klim Anlood for us, please?

rows.label: qst650313_msg0025
rows.name:
Broom Icicles! We need some
fresh Broom Icicles!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0026
rows.name:
I'd love it if you could bring back some
Emerald Snow... Oh, would you?

rows.label: qst650313_msg0027
rows.name:
Haha, totally!
Your wishes are my command!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0028
rows.name: That's very kind of you, dear.

rows.label: qst650313_msg0029
rows.name:
I hope you know your own limits,
though. I wouldn't want you to get
yourself hurt.

rows.label: qst650313_msg0030
rows.name:
Thanks for the warning, Zekey-boy.
They really dished 'em out!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0031
rows.name: Told you so!

rows.label: qst650313_msg0032
rows.name:
Still, it's not like I could turn any of
their requests down. Not when it's
stuff we do so well!
